chunks.text: Computer Vision, Section 001 - Announcements: Project Proposal Feedback Computer Vision, Section 001 - Announcements: Project Proposal Feedback Posted Wednesday, November 5, 2025 12:25 AM EST Hi everyone, We have finished our review of all the project proposals. We've sent individual emails with feedback and suggestions to teams where we had comments or wanted more clarification. If your team did not receive an email from us, that means your proposal looks good, and you're all set to move forward. As always, please reach out if you have any questions. Best, The TA Team (Austin, Georgy, and Siddharth) Computer Vision, Section 001 Go to Announcements >> You are receiving this message because you subscribed to receive instant notifications via email.
